# Beef Soya

> Source: https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1020289-beef-suya

- Short Ribs | 1.5 lbs, 1/4” chunks | 
- Peanut Oil | 1/4 cup | 
- Ginger Root | 2” grated | 
- Garlic | 2 cloves | 
- Salt |  | 
- Tomatoes | 2 count | 1/4” strips
- Red Onion | 1 count | Sliced rings
- Limes | 1 count |
- Peanuts | 1/4 cup | Toasted, chopped

## Seasoning

- Peanuts | 1/4 cup | Grind to powder
- Ginger | 1 tbsp | 
- Cayenne Pepper | 2 tsp |
- Paprika | 2 tap | 
- Onion Powder | 2 tsp | 
- Garlic Powder | 1 tsp | 
- Salt | 1 tsp | 
